A reminder to all mirrors.  We will be moving 3.15 and 3.16 off of cloudfront next week Tuesday May 30th.  Please update your rsyncs if you are using hard coded numerics before this date to not completely lose your repository.  If you do not update before we remove the Bioconductor versions, you will have to follow the instructions at https://github.com/Bioconductor/archive (Only once ever per release) to restore a package repository.  Reminder: Legacy Bioconductor releases are frozen and changes are not permitted at any time from maintainers.  You should only be syncing the current Bioconductor release and devel branches where changes are permitted.

Thank you.


Lori Shepherd - Kern

